About Us
Established in 1980, Oncor is one of the world’s oldest Christmas tree manufacturers. Our trees have an industry-leading product life of 30 or more years. Being responsible for our planet, all Oncor trees are eco-friendly and made from 100% non-toxic recycled PVC plastic.&nbsp;
USA Shipping
Free shipping is provided to the continental United States. We are not able to ship to Alaska or Hawaii. Orders are shipped with FedEx International Ground. Signature required service is available for free on request. Note: California buyers will receive a Proposition 65 label.&nbsp;
Global Shipping
We are now also able to offer Oncor Christmas trees to customers in all countries of the European Union and certain countries in East Asia. Please contact us for more information.&nbsp;
Payment
Payment is due within 2 business days after purchase. We only accept PayPal and payment by credit card or bank account through PayPal. Only Canadian customers are charged sales tax at the standard HST and GST rates. No sales tax is charged for international purchases.&nbsp;
Returns
Returns are accepted within 15 days of receipt or by December 25th, whichever comes first. We do not charge a restocking fee.
